Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)\be5\3c&H018662&}Bouře!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,750)\be5\3c&H00A1AC&}Blesky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,870)\be5\3c&H830186&}Přeludy!
